  "contents" : "<article>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 class=\"no-toc\" id=\"onchanges\">OnChanges</h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label interface\">interface</label>\n    \n    \n    \n    <span class=\"version\"></span>\n  </header>\n\n  \n  <!-- INFO BAR -->\n<section class=\"info-bar\">\n\n<table class=\"is-full-width\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n  <th data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4wfc14obst93bim1zva6hqjl0\">npm 包</th>\n  <td><a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/@angular/core\">@angular/core</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <th data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dkuxw56x8curh875ge5tvqede\">模块</th>\n  <td><code>import { <a href=\"api/core/OnChanges\" class=\"code-anchor\">OnChanges</a> } from <a href=\"api/core\">'@angular/core'</a>;</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <th data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ee4tba1a8v4m1low7rnv25o9l\">源码</th>\n  <td><a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/5.2.11/packages/core/src/metadata/lifecycle_hooks.ts#L18-L33\">core/src/metadata/lifecycle_hooks.ts</a></td>\n</tr>\n\n</tbody>\n</table>\n\n  \n<div class=\"what-it-does info-banner\">\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6zgemjsf1ljbkp9y63sk1vtm4\">当指令的任何数据绑定属性发生变化时调用的生命周期钩子。</p>\n\n</div>\n\n  \n  \n  <section class=\"interface-overview\">\n<h2 id=\"interface-overview\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"15ffnfvjx5orhxzfayretyfy4\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i>接口概览</h2>\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\">\ninterface <a href=\"api/core/OnChanges\" class=\"code-anchor\">OnChanges</a> { \n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/OnChanges#ngOnChanges\">ngOnChanges(changes: SimpleChanges): void</a>\n}\n</code-example>\n</section>\n  \n<section class=\"how-to-use\">\n  <h2 id=\"how-to-use\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"cflu95twzi71qd095ghj9h0y7\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i>使用方法</h2>\n  <code-example>\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({selector: 'my-cmp', template: `...`})\nclass MyComponent implements <a href=\"api/core/OnChanges\" class=\"code-anchor\">OnChanges</a> {\n  @<a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a>()\n  prop: number;\n\n  ngOnChanges(changes: <a href=\"api/core/SimpleChanges\" class=\"code-anchor\">SimpleChanges</a>) {\n    // changes.prop contains the old and the new value...\n  }\n}\n\n</code-example>\n\n</section>\n\n\n  \n  \n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ar5q09mdsagdppsbze96eagxl\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i>说明</h2>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4nm8fed4ccu645riexn9whi8w\"><code>ngOnChanges</code> 在数据绑定属性被检查后立即调用，在视图和内容子元素被检查之前调用（如果至少有一个子元素发生了变化）。 \n<code>changes</code> 参数包含已更改的属性。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"5n0b050hn6d1pw9hj82fqo886\">请参见 \n<a href=\"guide/lifecycle-hooks#onchanges\">\"生命周期钩子指南\"</a>。</p>\n\n</section>\n\n  \n  \n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n  <h2 id=\"class-implementations\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"daenb2ecubh5cf0evvwqtqnnm\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i>类实现</h2>\n  <ul class=\"descendants class\">\n  \n    <li>\n      <pre class=\"prettyprint lang-ts\"><code><a href=\"api/upgrade/static/UpgradeComponent\" class=\"code-anchor\">UpgradeComponent</a></code></pre>\n      \n  \n  \n\n    </li>\n  \n  </ul>\n  \n\n  \n\n<section class=\"instance-members\">\n  <h2 id=\"members\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"e62kgm2ztk7rgk6auybfiv91o\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i>成员</h2>\n  \n    <div class=\"instance-member\">\n  <a id=\"ngOnChanges\"></a>\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">ngOnChanges(changes: <a href=\"api/core/SimpleChanges\" class=\"code-anchor\">SimpleChanges</a>): void</code-example></div>\n\n    \n    \n  \n</section>\n\n\n\n\n\n</section></article>\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common/NgComponentOutlet\n - api/common/NgForOf\n - api/common/NgTemplateOutlet\n - api/core\n - api/core/DoCheck\n - api/core/SimpleChanges\n - api/forms/FormControlDirective\n - api/forms/FormControlName\n - api/forms/FormGroupDirective\n - api/forms/MaxLengthValidator\n - api/forms/MinLengthValidator\n - api/forms/NgModel\n - api/forms/PatternValidator\n - api/router/RouterLinkActive\n - api/router/RouterLinkWithHref\n - api/upgrade/static/UpgradeComponent\n - guide/component-interaction\n - guide/lifecycle-hooks\n - guide/reactive-forms\n - guide/styleguide\n - guide/testing\n - guide/upgrade\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/core\n - api/core/Component\n - api/core/Input\n - api/core/OnChanges#class-implementations\n - api/core/OnChanges#description\n - api/core/OnChanges#how-to-use\n - api/core/OnChanges#interface-overview\n - api/core/OnChanges#members\n - api/core/OnChanges#ngOnChanges\n - api/core/OnChanges#onchanges\n - api/core/SimpleChanges\n - api/upgrade/static/UpgradeComponent\n - guide/lifecycle-hooks#onchanges\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/5.2.11/packages/core/src/metadata/lifecycle_hooks.ts#L18-L33\n - https://www.npmjs.com/package/@angular/core\n-->"
